1cPreach to people once a week every Friday. If you refuse, then two times. If you desire more, then three times. Do not make people averse to this Quran. Do not come to people while they are talking and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27542,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/13\/best-answer-fool-silence\/","url_meta":{"origin":25127,"position":2},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Debate: Best answer to a fool is silence","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Imam al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah be pleased with him, said in his poetry, \u201cIf a fool speaks to you, do not answer him, for the best answer is silence. If you speak to him, you have delighted him. If you leave him, he nearly dies in anguish.\u201d Source: Di\u0304wa\u0304n al-Ima\u0304m al-Sha\u0304fi\u2019i\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24671,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/04\/10\/sufyan-on-silence-being-silent-for-long-periods-is-the-key-to-worship\/","url_meta":{"origin":25127,"position":3},"title":"Sufyan on Silence: Being silent for long periods is the key to worship","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 10, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Humaydi reported: Sufyan Ath-Thawri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIt is said that observing long periods of silence is the key to worship.\u201d Source: al-S\u0323am